title: Spider-Man: Across the Spider-Verse is a (Flawed) Masterpiece
description:
This video is sponsored by Brilliant. Go to https://brilliant.org/Midnight/ and sign up for free 30 day trial, the first 200 people that go to that link will get 20% off the annual Premium subscription.
Miles Morales is back in a Spider-Verse adventure even more visually impressive than the first. In this video, I go over it all, from Gwen Stacy to Peter Parker to Spider-Man 2099.
